review_id: Il est un lieu de rencontre ideal des villageois. Il sert de relais entre les passagers qui traversent Tafoughalt et empruntent le chemin intercommunal reliant  la RN 25 et le CW 107. Il est situe a un jet de pierre de la poste, la pharmacie, le CEM Meddour et l'ecole des freres Salemkour.

review_translated_text: It is an ideal meeting place for villagers. It serves as a relay between passengers who cross Tafoughalt and take the intercommunal path connecting the RN 25 and the CW 107. It is located a stone's throw from the post office, the pharmacy, the CEM Meddour and the Salemkour brothers' school.
